{"tid":265284,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方宣佈雲格續約至2019","createTime":"2017-05-31T13:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T13:47:34.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d52c0f99436e3079ad65b88933fd494d8eea871","tid":265284,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴官方終於向外公佈。雖然今季面對不少質疑，惟球會高層仍對他投下信心一票，雲格事後在官網表示：「我愛這球會，而我對未來既樂觀又期待。我們正努力在各方面求進，球隊本身已經很強，只要在各方面補充一下兵力，我們絕對可以更成功。我很多謝高層對我的信任，Stan也盡一切努力去助我們爭取錦標。我知道球迷想要什麼，這也是我想要的。」<br />\n<br />\n790 - Arsene Wenger has taken charge of 790 Premier League games as a manager; only Sir Alex Ferguson has managed more (810). Longevity. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/Q5Had8l2Wc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FQ5Had8l2Wc&d=SKgAetXxONuB2%2Fe424LtrQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=564d4b7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/Q5Had8l2Wc</a><br />\n&mdash; OptaJoe (@OptaJoe) May 31, 2017<br />\n雲格續約後，其首要任務就是留住奧斯爾及阿歷斯山齊士兩名主力，他們合約仍有一年便到期，若不續約便很可能離隊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87035470606710ee3e11d18d7dc20a84c12bb16f","tid":265284,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"雲加已戰勝歸來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暴龍哥掃進棺材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}